{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_vrtx_01GdLwBju19sbwqPw58cEkZX","type":"tool_result","content":"update: generate update-manifests update-bindata ## Update all generated code and manifests.\n\n.PHONY: update-manifests\nupdate-manifests: $(HELM) $(JSONNET) $(YQ) ## Update cert-manager and istio-csr operand manifests.\n\thack/update-cert-manager-manifests.sh $(CERT_MANAGER_VERSION)\n\thack/update-istio-csr-manifests.sh $(ISTIO_CSR_VERSION)\n---\n# BUNDLE_GEN_FLAGS are the flags passed to the operator-sdk generate bundle command\n\t$(CONTROLLER_GEN) rbac:roleName=manager-role crd webhook paths=\"$(PROJECT_ROOT)/...\" \\\n\t\toutput:crd:artifacts:config=$(PROJECT_ROOT)/config/crd/bases \\\n.PHONY: generate\ngenerate: generate-fakes $(CONTROLLER_GEN) ## Generate code containing DeepCopy, DeepCopyInto, and DeepCopyObject method implementations.\n.PHONY: generate-fakes\ngenerate-fakes: ## Generate fake implementations for testing using counterfeiter.\n\tgo generate ./...\ntest: manifests generate vet test-apis test-unit ## Run tests.\n\t-oc get crd | grep -i cert\nbuild: generate fmt vet build-operator ## Build operator binary with all checks and code generation.\nrun: manifests generate fmt vet ## Run the operator from your host (for development).\nbundle: $(OPERATOR_SDK) $(KUSTOMIZE) manifests ## Generate bundle manifests and metadata, then validate generated files.\n\t$(OPERATOR_SDK) generate kustomize manifests -q\n\t$(KUSTOMIZE) build config/manifests | $(OPERATOR_SDK) generate bundle $(BUNDLE_GEN_FLAGS)\n\thack/verify-deepcopy.sh\nupdate: generate update-manifests update-bindata ## Update all generated code and manifests.\nclean: ## Clean up generated files and build artifacts.","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"09f1e293-33ec-4a3a-90a4-e6b51e0146dd","uuid":"8812aebd-c40c-4fc1-9f1c-5811401bd06b","timestamp":"2026-07-20T17:40:50.092Z","tool_use_result":{"stdout":"update: generate update-manifests update-b